# Project scripts

- **Never edit** `scripts/aem.js`
- Keep Trusted Types policy and load phases in `scripts.js`
- Eager: decorate + first section; Lazy: header/sections/footer; Delayed: 3s defer
- Preserve `decorateMain` export for fragment loading
- Avoid heavy work on the critical path
